    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty bleak view lol. but wouldn't someone say that the failures aren't really the UN's fault, but just because world powers won't play nice? like is it actually a failure of the institution itself, or is the institution just a mirror of how messy global politics already are?",
